	   Syed Kamal Bakht, MP (AL- Satkhira-1), has said that local
leaders of opposition BNP, Jatiya Party and Jamaat are out to
tarnish the image of the ruling party propagating false'
information over the possession of nine shrimp farms at Debhata and
