<TEXT>
	   The visiting Saudi Parliamentary delegation made a courtesy call
on President Justice Shahabuddin Ahmed and Prime Minister Sheikh
Hasina yesterday.
	   Welcoming the delegation President Shahabuddin said the existing
bonds of relationship between Bangladesh and Saudi Arabia are
characterised by utmost cordiality, mutual understanding and ever
deepening brotherly ties based on common religious faith, shared
history and culture.
	   The President said beyond the orbit of political relations, the
two countries' cooperation in economic and financial fields has
developed to a substantial proportion.
