<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-Sports-Tennis-French Open, Results 3rd ADD </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
PARIS: 6-0, 6-3 Men's Singles Fourth Round 
</HEADLINE>
RETRANSMITTING     
<TEXT>
	   Filip Dewulf, Belgium, def. Francisco Clavet, Spain, 7-5, 6-3,
6-1.
  Women's Doubles  
  Third Round  
	   Martina Hingis, Switzerland, and Jana Novotna (2), Czech
Republic, def. Kristine Kunce, Australia, and Corina Morariu,
United States, 6-0, 6-1.
  Mixed Doubles  
  Third Round  
	   Lori McNeil, United States, and Joshua Eagle (15), Australia,
def. Rika Hiraki, Japan, and Paul Kilderry, Australia, 6-2, 6-2.
	   Caroline Vis, Netherlands, and John-Laffnie De Jager (16), South
Africa, def. Anne-Gaelle Sidot, France, and Sebastien Grosjean,
France, 6-7 (2-7), 6-2, 6-3.
  Boys' Singles  
  First Round  
	   Lars Ubel, Germany, def. Emiliano Redondi, Argentina, 6-4, 6-2.
	   Simone Amorico, United States, def. Jean-Christophe Faurel,
France, 3-6, 7-6 (7-3), 6-0.
