Palm oil, NEW STRAITS TIMES-MANAGEMENT TIMES  
   xfdws PALM-OIL sked
   Emerging Markets Datafile
   June 01, 1998
   NEW STRAITS TIMES-MANAGEMENT TIMES
   ENGLISH
