Market upside limited in coming weeks, NEW STRAITS TIMES-MANAGEMENT TIMES  
   xfdws MARKET-UPSIDE-LIMITED sked
   Emerging Markets Datafile
   June 01, 1998
   NEW STRAITS TIMES-MANAGEMENT TIMES
