Kit For Special People, MALAYSIAN BUSINESS  
   xfdws KIT-FOR-SPECIAL-PEOPLE sked
   Emerging Markets Datafile
   May 16, 1998
   MALAYSIAN BUSINESS
   ENGLISH
	   COPYRIGHT 1998 BY WORLDSOURCES, INC., A JOINT VENTURE OF FDCH,
