	   SECRETARY Chua Meng Meng was the grand prize winner of the HP
PhotoRet II Spot the Aliens contest organised by Hewlett-Packard
Sales (M) Sdn Bhd (HPSM).
	   With her slogan ``bright and beautiful or dark and sombre, every
