<TEXT>
	   SCS Computer Systems Sdn Bhd, has been appointed by Gentia
Software (Asia) Ltd as the distributor of its business intelligence
solutions in the East and West Malaysia markets. The agreement was
signed by Mr Looi Kien Leong, chief executive officer and managing
director of SCS and Mr Tay Guan Mong, regional director of Gentia
Software Asia.
	   Gentia is a powerful, flexible environment for the development
of strategic business intelligence applications. Designed for
today's networked enterprise, Gentia breaks through platform,
operating system and database barriers. It is able to access,
organise and structure information from every data source,
database, application and type of file, as well as build `knowledge
marts' that deliver information to decision makers.
	   Gentia has dual headquarters in Boston and London and operates
in over 20 countries worldwide.
	   
