<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-01-06 12:13:00 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
w1019  wstm-
u s     BC-Sports-FieldHockey-Wo     06-01 0061
