crutches, others break into a run as international aid helicopters
land Monday in the remote region of Afghanistan devastated by an
earthquake that killed more than 3,000 people. AFGHANISTAN-QUAKE.
Lead has moved. By Phil Goodwin. AP Photo ISL102.
