<HEADLINE>
PARIS: France, Mixed Doubles Second Round 
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
	   Iva Majoli, Croatia, and Todd Martin, United States, def.
Natasha Zvereva, Belarus, and Andrew Florent (6), Australia, 6-4,
7-6 (7-4).
  Mixed Doubles  
  Third Round  
	   Manon Bollegraf, Netherlands, and Rick Leach (2), United States,
def. Alexia Dechaume-Balleret, France, and Jean-Philippe Fleurian,
France, 6-1, 2-6, 6-4.
  Boys' Singles  
  Second Round  
