<HEADLINE>
MALAYSIA
</HEADLINE>
Three sen off every litre of Esso petrol for 16 days, NEW STRAITS TIMES-MANAGEMENT TIMES  
   xfdws LITRE-OF-ESSO-PETROL sked
   Emerging Markets Datafile
   May 30, 1998
