DAP urges emergency meet over negative GDP growth, NEW STRAITS TIMES- MANAGEMENT TIMES  
   xfdws NEGATIVE-GDP-GROWTH sked
   Emerging Markets Datafile
   June 01, 1998
   NEW STRAITS TIMES-MANAGEMENT TIMES
   ENGLISH
	   COPYRIGHT 1998 BY WORLDSOURCES, INC., A JOINT VENTURE OF FDCH,
