<BODY>
<SLUG> TRADITIONAL-WELCOME sked </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
MALAYSIA
</HEADLINE>
Kelantan lays out traditional welcome for PM, NEW STRAITS TIMES- MANAGEMENT TIMES  
