<BODY>
<SLUG> MOVE-TO-MEET-BUILDER sked </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
MALAYSIA
</HEADLINE>
Move to meet builder over abandoned project, NEW STRAITS TIMES- MANAGEMENT TIMES  
   xfdws MOVE-TO-MEET-BUILDER sked
   Emerging Markets Datafile
   May 30, 1998
   NEW STRAITS TIMES-MANAGEMENT TIMES
   ENGLISH
