<TEXT>
	   SELANGOR Menteri Besar Datuk Abu Hassan Omar will launch the
Commonwealth Games time capsule at the Kelana Jaya recreation park
on Thursday.
	   Petaling Jaya Municipal Council president Datuk Mohamad Nor
Bador said the time capsule was aimed at educating the public on
the event.
	   He said the capsule would have the latest information on the
Games.
	   ``We are proud to use the Kelana Jaya Stadium and PKNS field for
the games,'' he added.
	   He urged councillors and the public to be present at the
launching ceremony.
	   
