	   ALAM Flora Sdn Bhd will take over urban services in Kajang,
Semenyih, Beranang, Ulu Semenyih, Hulu Langat and Cheras areas
under the Kajang Municipal Council's jurisdiction, from July 1.
	   The company will also buy over all 16 lorries and other
