improve cleanliness in Kajang and other urban centres in the
district.
	   She said the Kajang Municipal Council had about 53,000 property
holdings which needed such services.
	   She said services provided by Alam Flora included rubbish
collection, drain cleaning and grass cutting along roads.
	   She said before the Commonwealth Games, the company would also
provide special services in areas outside the council's
jurisdiction including grass cutting along Jalan Balakong and other
roads under private concessionaires.
	   Kamariah said the council would launch road shows, meet local
social organisations and brief residents according to zones before
the takeover.
