w1694  wstm-
r f     BC-Nikko-Travelers 4thLd-Writethru   06-01 0679
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-Nikko-Travelers, 4th Ld-Writethru,0674 </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
Travelers Group takes 25 percent stake in top Japanese brokerage 
</HEADLINE>
Eds: RETRANSMITS to correct writethru sequence for some points
By CHESTER DAWSON
Associated Press Writer
